# Technology Stack

## Core Technologies
- [Next.js](mdc:https:/nextjs.org) - React framework with App Router structure
- [TypeScript](mdc:https:/www.typescriptlang.org) - For type safety
- [Bun](mdc:https:/bun.sh) - JavaScript runtime and package manager
- [Tailwind CSS](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - For styling
- [Shadcn UI](mdc:components.json) - Component library built on Radix UI

## State Management
- [Zustand](mdc:src/store/useAuth.ts) - Simple state management solution
  - Various stores in [src/store/](mdc:src/store) directory
  - Persistent storage with localStorage

## APIs & Data Fetching
- [Axios](mdc:src/lib/api.ts) - HTTP client for API requests
- [TanStack Query](mdc:https:/tanstack.com/query/latest) - For data fetching and cache management

## UI Components & Libraries
- [Radix UI](mdc:https:/www.radix-ui.com) - Headless UI components
- [Lucide React](mdc:https:/lucide.dev/guide/packages/lucide-react) - Icon library
- [Tailwind Merge](mdc:https:/github.com/dcastil/tailwind-merge) - Merges Tailwind CSS classes
- [Class Variance Authority](mdc:https:/cva.style/docs) - For component variants
- [React Hook Form](mdc:https:/react-hook-form.com) - Form management
- [Zod](mdc:https:/zod.dev) - Schema validation

## Authentication
- Custom authentication system with Laravel Sanctum
- CSRF token management through [src/lib/api.ts](mdc:src/lib/api.ts)
